text: This was my fantastic #ARW19 panel: Columbus Mayor James Lienhoop; Danny Lopez, deputy chief of staff to Gov. Holcomb; Roberto Salinas Leon of Mexico Business Forum; and Lilly’s Tiffany Benjamin.

text: I’m incredibly honored to have spent a little time today with former Sen Dick Lugar and former Rep Lee Hamilton, two of the most influential and upstanding people I’ve ever met. #ARW19
author: LWeidenbener

text: Ran into this old friend - Paul Helmke - at the America’s Role in the World Conference at the Hamilton Lugar School of Global and International Studies. Paul was the Fort Wayne mayor when I was a reporter there. #ARW19
